just go with it is a 2011 american romantic comedy film directed by dennis dugan , written by allan loeb and timothy dowling and starring adam sandler ( who also co-produced ) , jennifer aniston , nicole kidman , nick swardson and brooklyn decker . the film is based on the 1969 film cactus flower which was adapted from an earlier broadway stage play written by abe burrows , which in turn was based upon the french play fleur de cactus . production of the film began on march 2 , 2010 . the film was released on february 11 , 2011 by columbia pictures in north america . the film grossed over $ 214 million , making it a box office success - however , the film received negative reviews from critics and won two golden raspberry awards for worst actor and worst director .